-- Ram Power CEO and CFO to Depart, Seeks Buyer for Geysers Project
-- B y   T i n a   D a v i s
-- 2013-01-28T13:08:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-28/ram-power-ceo-and-cfo-to-depart-seeks-buyer-for-geysers-project.html
Ram Power Corp. (RPG) , a Reno, Nevada-
based renewable-energy company, will cut staff and its chief
executive officer and chief financial officer will depart.  The company is seeking a partner or buyer for its Geysers
project and is attempting to refinance a C$50 million corporate
credit facility, according to a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tina Davis at 
 tinadavis@bloomberg.net  